I bring you an AirPods Pro 2 USB-C unboxing, giving you a look at everything that comes in the box, including that high quality braided USB-C to USB-C cable. original_client_text.markup_text:
The new AirPods Pro 2nd generation have finally gained a USB-C charging case update, but @apple has secretly packed two game-changing new features into these earbuds as well!

I bring you an AirPods Pro 2 USB-C unboxing, giving you a look at everything that comes in the box, including that high quality braided USB-C to USB-C cable.

Then, we go over the two new features Apple didn't tell you about during the iPhone 15 keynote - dust resistance and ultra low latency lossless audio support when used with Apple Vision Pro. For the first time ever, you can experience 20-bit, 48kHz lossless audio completely wirelessly with the new AirPods Pro 2nd gen with USB-C case.
